---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Trademark Disclaimer — AI Zest"
  description="AI Zest trademark disclaimer — all product names, logos, and brands are property of their respective owners."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 sm:py-12">
    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <nav class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-[#3B82F6]">Home</a>
      <span>/</span>
      <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-medium">Trademark Disclaimer</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Trademark Disclaimer</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 mb-10">Last updated: June 26, 2026</p>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-amber-50 dark:bg-amber-900/10 border border-amber-100 dark:border-amber-900/20">
        <p class="text-sm text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-300 leading-relaxed">
          All product names, logos, brands, trademarks, and registered trademarks are the property of their respective owners. Their use on this website is for identification and informational purposes only and does not imply endorsement, sponsorship, or affiliation with AI Zest.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">1. Third-Party Brands</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        AI Zest is an independent review and comparison website. We reference third-party products and services solely for the purpose of providing information, reviews, and comparisons to our readers.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        Brands referenced on this site include but are not limited to: OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, Meta, Midjourney, Stability AI, Runway, Cursor, GitHub, and others. All rights to these names and marks belong to their respective holders.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">2. No Affiliation</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        Unless expressly stated otherwise, AI Zest is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by any of the companies whose products are reviewed or mentioned on this website. All reviews and ratings represent our independent opinions based on available information and research.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">3. Fair Use</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        Use of third-party trademarks on this website is for nominative and descriptive purposes only — to identify and refer to the products and services being reviewed, compared, or discussed. This constitutes fair use under applicable trademark laws. We do not use any trademark in a way that would cause confusion or suggest sponsorship by the trademark holder.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">4. Corrections</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        If you believe any trademark or brand representation on this site is inaccurate or requires clarification, please contact us at <a href="mailto:admin@aizest.net" class="text-[#3B82F6] hover:underline">admin@aizest.net</a> and we will address it promptly.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
